       .when(jmsTemplate) &lt;- a mock is expected to be used here
       .convertAndSend(queue, obj, messagePostProcessor);
```
You&#39;re right that the last parameter is the actual problem since different instances are being used.

The first instance is defined by your lambda in the test:
```
