```
And the second one is defined with the other lambda when you perform the call to `jmsTemplate.convertAndSend(..., ..., message -&gt; {...})`

Posibly you&#39;re getting that error because you&#39;re verifying that the `jmsTemplate.convertAndSend(...)` was called with the params you defined in the tests.
Something like:
```
